# Read-Before-Write Rule

Before modifying any file:

1. Identify boundaries — interfaces, types, schemas
2. Read upstream via @filename
3. State signatures in plan
4. Then edit

## Critique Checklist

- Null/empty values
- Network timeouts
- Race conditions
- Unhandled exceptions

## UTF-8 & Verification

- Write all text files as UTF-8 without BOM (never UTF-16)
- Never mark BUILD_PLAN tasks complete without running validate scripts
- Run `scripts/validate-bootstrap.sh` after creating Sprint 0 artifacts
- Sprint 0 sign-off (canonical): `validate-bootstrap.sh --quick`, `feature-gate.sh --stack <active>`, `check-github-ci.sh --wait 300`, `check-license-compliance.sh` — see `BUILD_PLAN.md` Child Repo Playbook
